This could be a syntactical error. In your line ```const file = fs.readFileSync(&#39;src/atoms/${newFileName}/${newFileName}.js&#39;);``` are you sure you are using *back-ticks* and not single quotes?

This might solve it: 

```const file = fs.readFileSync(`src/atoms/${newFileName}/${newFileName}.js`);```

back-tick key is usually on the top left corner just below the Esc key and to the left of number 1 key.

